§7§oIt may be a good time to start filling up a bunch of books!

§fThe potential energy of the Book of the Dead, while having the capability of performing rituals touching the higher-order dimensions, exists itself in the string-theory space. 
I have not really thought about building devices or artifacts working in these higher dimensions, as I was scared of starting more conflicts against the Old Ones, but I think it may be time to experiment more with this!
